<A NAME="18416"></A><FONT FACE="helvetica, arial, sans-serif" SIZE="-1"><zparagraph>
The ShowTime Portlet allows you to display time based on the selected time zone. This portlet also allows you to compare time between two different timezones. </zparagraph>
</FONT>
<P>

<A NAME="13519"></A><FONT FACE="helvetica, arial, sans-serif" SIZE="-1"><zparagraph>
